works.description: For biking buffs who treasure their Harleys, but are looking to explore the custom-made territory to add to their rich collection, we introduce you to the “Unorthodox” – the latest creation by London-based custom Harley-Davidson designer Charlie Stockwell of Warr’s Harley-Davidson. The new, custom Harley is strikingly different from the other designs offered ever from Stockwell and Warr’s H-D. Stockwell is well known for his award-winning and trend-setting vintage designs, but with the bespoke Harley-Davidson Unorthodox,
